title: Lester vs Lackey matches former Red Sox teammates
text:
> Top News Lester vs Lackey matches former Red Sox teammates St. Louis Cardinals Game 1 starter John Lackey walks to the bull pen with his six-year-old son, Carter, during the team workout, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015 in St. Louis. The Cardinals will face the Chicago Cubs, for the first time in post-season history, in the National League Division Series.
